Tech Lead Notes — license summary

This repository combines content under two Creative Commons licenses.
Per-chunk and per-card license is authoritative — see the
`license:` field in each Markdown file's YAML frontmatter and the
[Sources manifest](docs/sources.md) for the canonical mapping.

================================================================
