================================================================
3. Combined dumps (llms-full.txt, full HTML site)
================================================================

The combined corpus dump (llms-full.txt) and the rendered HTML
site combine CC-BY and CC-BY-SA material. Per the ShareAlike
clause of CC BY-SA 4.0, the combined whole is effectively
CC BY-SA 4.0. Individual files within the corpus retain their
original licenses, which can be checked via the `license:`
frontmatter field in each Markdown chunk.

================================================================
4. Editorial scripts and tooling
