ingest_scrum_guide.py, ingest_scrum_guide_expanded.py,
split_dora_metrics.py, build_llms_txt.py) and the MkDocs
configuration (mkdocs.yml, pyproject.toml, .github/workflows/)
are licensed under MIT for permissive reuse:

